This is my dwm configuration suite:

- The main config.h, defining keyboard shortcuts, layouts, and general
  behavior
- A status line application that shows battery status, battery charge,
  the date, and the time
- A desktop session file, which calls...
- A session script that starts dwm, turns on an ACPI manager, sets the
  desktop background, and starts a file manager daemon
- An X.org font configuration file to use my favorite font (DejaVu Sans
  Mono within dwm)
